Happy birthday to the love of my life! As we celebrate another year together, I’m reminded of the incredible journey we’ve shared so far, filled with moments of joy and challenges. Regardless, there is nobody else I’d rather have as my partner on this adventure than you! Here’s to many more years of love, laughter, and overcoming any obstacles that may come our way. You are my rock, my happiness, and my forever. 🎉❤️🎂

Quiero que sepas que siempre serás mi bebé que te amo incondicionalmente y que verte feliz es mi más grande felicidad, que ser tu mamá es un privilegio🤍 Eres luz mi princesa amada  que sigas brillando siempre amor mío 🤍🤍 gracias Familia por estar y poder celebrar juntos este cumpleaños 🎂 ‘Lord knows the best thing that I’ll ever do will be growing up raising you’ #birthdaygirl #disneyworld #birthdayindisneyland #firstborndaughter #4thbday
